BEING AS AN OCEN is an American melodic and post hardcore band from Alpine, California, formed in 2011, after the band VANGUARD, in which were all founding members, disbanded. Before this recent album, they have released of two full-length albums: "Dear G-d..." and "How We Both Wondrously Perish" - this album (which was released in May 2014) charted at number 57 on the Billboard 200 in America.
Current members are: Joel Quartuccio (lead vocal), Tyler Ross (lead guitar, backing vocal), Ralph Sica (bass), Michael McGough (rhythm guitar, clean vocals) and Connor Denis (drums & percussion).
Past members: Shad Hamawe - drums, percussion (2011-2013), Jacob Prest - rhythm guitar (2012-2013)
